eNCA reporter Liundokuhle Xulu is on that story. EMALAHLENI - ANC in Mpumalanga is mourning the death of Emalahleni mayor Linah Malatjie. She died in a car crash on Monday morning, along with her husband. Their car collided with another vehicle between KwaMhlanga and Emalahleni. Family members say they are shattered by the news of her death. The family says it will give an update about funeral arrangements.